ore the medical team patched up the bleeding cut above her right eye, which was immediately swollen.\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 583, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 442, \"end\": 448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8479165735431077, \"rank\": 0.1556537337252867, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the medical team\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 503}, {\"ngram\": \"the bleeding cut\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 531}, {\"ngram\": \"her right eye\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 551}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'She left to get medical attention but she is back,' said Rich Lerner, a commentator for United States broadcaster NBC.\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 704, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 643, \"end\": 647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rich_Hardbeck\", \"score\": 0.9999996002473726, \"rank\": 3.9544303202564576e-07, \"text\": \"Rich\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rich_Hardbeck\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rich_Hardbeck\"}, {\"begin\": 648, \"end\": 654, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Jay_Lerner\", \"score\": 0.999850294407886, \"rank\": 0.00014971931476766043, \"text\": \"Lerner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Jay_Lerner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Jay_Lerner\"}, {\"begin\": 674, \"end\": 687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9964374358426257, \"rank\": 0.002824765587264692, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_St